/*
Mathematical specification (applies to both kernels):

Preconditions:
- N >= 0, D >= 1, top_k >= 0
- Pointers Xdata (size N*D) and labelData (size N) are valid device pointers
- For all 0 <= r < N, 0 <= labelData[r] < D
- accuracy points to a valid device-side integer (cleared to 0 prior to kernel launch)

