Kernel: accuracy_kernel
- Optimizations:
  - Broadcast label and label_pred via shared memory to eliminate 256x redundant loads per row
    (addresses stalls at PC SUMMARY lines 25, 26, 29 via reduced L1TEX scoreboard waits).
