  This satisfies the postcondition for position i. Thus I_{i+1} holds.
- After completing the inner loop, all positions in [0, B*T-1] for block b satisfy the postcondition.
  Therefore, I_b progresses to I_{b+1}.
- By induction on b, after all blocks, the postcondition holds for all processed elements.

